<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="text-align: center; padding: 20px;">
        <img src="cid:logo" alt="Logo" style="width: 150px; height: auto;">
    </div>

  <h2 style="color: #2c3e50;">Hello {{studentName}},</h2>

  <p>Thank you for attending a session with <strong>{{tutorName}}</strong>!</p>

  <h3>Session Details:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Course:</strong> {{courseName}}</li>
    <li><strong>Topics:</strong> {{topics}}</li>
    <li><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</li>
    <li><strong>Start Time:</strong> {{time}}</li>
    <li><strong>Duration:</strong> {{duration}} hrs</li>
  </ul>

  <p>We would love to hear your feedback. Please click the link below to leave your feedback for the session:</p>

  <a href={{feedbackUrl}} style="display:inline-block;padding:10px 20px;background-color:#273bae;color:white;text-decoration:none;border-radius:5px;">Leave Feedback</a>

  <p>Thank you!</p>
</div>
